headline: Sempra Named One of the World's Best Companies by TIME Magazine
summary: Sempra (NYSE: SRE) (BMV: SRE) has been recognized by TIME Magazine as one of the World's Best Companies for 2024. The recognition, presented by TIME and Statista Inc., places Sempra on a list of top performing companies across the globe based on employee satisfaction, revenue growth and sustainability transparency.
